# Evidence – API Security Risk Analysis

This folder contains supporting evidence collected during **Task 3: API Security Risk Analysis**, completed as part of the **Cyber SecurityInternship Program at Future Interns**.

The evidence supports the findings documented in the API security risk analysis report.

---

## 📌 Evidence Included
- Screenshots of API requests and responses captured using Postman
- Observations of HTTP status codes and returned data
- Proof of unauthenticated access to API endpoints

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- Postman (for API request and response analysis)

---

## ⚠️ Ethical Notice
All evidence was collected using **read-only and non-intrusive techniques** on a publicly accessible demo API.  
No exploitation, data modification, or harmful activity was performed.

